post_text:
Latinos have a history of being undercounted in the Census, resulting in disadvantages that impact their families, communities, and neighborhoods.

Join Univision as they spearhead Census Week, from July 6-10th, to bring awareness about the importance of the #2020Census. univision.com/censo

@UnivisionContigo #CuentaConmigo

